  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK312">
<l>kaṟuttiṉṉā ceytavaṟ kaṇṇu maṟuttiṉṉā</l>
<l>ceyyāmai mācaṟṟār kōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the determination of the spotless not to do evil, even in return, to those who have cherished enmity and done them evil.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
